---
import FileLines from '@assets/icons/FileLines.astro'
import MailSolid from '@assets/icons/MailSolid.astro'
---

<section
    id="contact"
    aria-labelledby="contact-heading"
    class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 bg-bg"
>
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none"
        aria-hidden="true"
    >
        <div class="w-1/2 h-1/2 bg-primary/5 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center space-y-10">
        <header class="space-y-6">
            <h2
                id="contact-heading"
                class="font-bold tracking-tight text-text leading-[1.1]
               text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem)]"
            >
                Â¿Trabajamos juntos?
            </h2>

            <p
                class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mx-auto max-w-prose
               text-[clamp(1rem,1.3vw,1.25rem)]"
            >
                Siempre estoy abierto a discutir nuevos proyectos, ideas
                creativas u oportunidades para ser parte de tus visiones.
            </p>
        </header>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6">
            <a
                href="mailto:contact@nicolasladner.dev"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2
               px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold
               text-[clamp(0.95rem,1vw,1.05rem)]
               bg-primary text-black
               shadow-glow hover:shadow-glow-hover
               transition-all duration-300
               hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
                <MailSolid />
                Enviar mensaje
            </a>

            <a
                href="/cv_ariel-ladner.pdf"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2
               px-8 py-4 rounded-lg
               text-[clamp(0.95rem,1vw,1.05rem)]
               font-medium
               border border-white/10
               text-white hover:bg-white/5
               transition-all duration-300"
            >
                <FileLines />
                Descargar CV
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
